OL,3,CGround-mounted solar farm in Jersey
OL,4,Ccould drive down energy prices
OL,6,FMr Ambler said: "One of the challenges
OL,7,Fthat we have with these sorts of
OL,8,Fdevelopments is that the cost of the
OL,9,Fenergy produced is still higher than
OL,10,Fimporting from France but the strategy
OL,11,Fis to get into this area of project,
OL,12,Fdrive the cost down and make it more
OL,13,Feconomically viable vis-a-vis imported
OL,14,Fpower."
OL,16,FThe JE boss confirmed that the price
OL,17,Fof electricity is more likely to come
OL,18,Fdown if similar developments are built
OL,19,Fin other parts of the island.
