OL,3,CGround-mounted solar farm in Jersey
OL,4,Ccould drive down energy prices
OL,6,FJE currently has two other sites in
OL,7,FJersey earmarked for ground-mounted
OL,8,Fsolar energy production and is also
OL,9,Fworking on installing more roof-based
OL,10,Fsolar panels across the island.
OL,12,FEarlier this week, JE increased
OL,13,Fislanders' electricity tariff by 7.5%
OL,14,Ffrom January 2025, adding around #2
OL,15,Fextra per week to the average
OL,16,Fhousehold bill.
OL,18,FThe company blamed higher than normal
OL,19,Fwholesale energy prices for the hike.
