OL,3,CGround-mounted solar farm in Jersey
OL,4,Ccould drive down energy prices
OL,6,FMr Ambler says that while the
OL,7,F"community-based" solar development in
OL,8,FSt Clement is a step in the right
OL,9,Fdirection towards driving down prices
OL,10,Ffor consumers, it is not an easy fix.
OL,12,FHe said: "There's no golden nugget
OL,13,Fsolution here. What we're trying to do
OL,14,Fis to develop a package of solutions
OL,15,Fand they all have a role at a level.
OL,17,F"One of the other really important
OL,18,Fthings about this development is that
OL,19,Fit is, in a sense, temporary.
