OL,3,CGround-mounted solar farm in Jersey
OL,4,Ccould drive down energy prices
OL,6,F"Yes, it's got a 40-year life, but at
OL,7,Fthe end of that 40-year period we can
OL,8,Fremove the solar panels and we can
OL,9,Frestore the site to bare earth."
OL,11,FMr Ambler added that while Jersey sees
OL,12,Fenough sunshine in the summer to
OL,13,Fproduce solar energy, the island will
OL,14,Fstill need to be connected to the
OL,15,Fwider grid in the winter when daylight
OL,16,Fhours are significantly reduced.
